Question: Explain to a younger friend how to apply for a college.
Answer:
Firstly, you need to work hard during the high school to get a nice grade. It is really helpful in you application to a college. Secondly, try to do as much as volunteer job at your spare time. This can show your social responsibility. Last but nit least, find your special character and show it in your applications.Take it easy in your interviews and Good luck.